course.subject: ELEC
course.name: Computer Engineering Final Year Project I
course.description: [Also COMP 4991] Each Computer Engineering student is required to take COMP 4991, 4992 and 4993/ELEC 4905, 4915 and 4925. The project is conducted under the supervision of faculty members from the Department of Computer Science and Engineering and/or the Department of Electronic and Computer Engineering. May be graded PP.
